law.history: Repealed 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 406, sec. 336, effective January 1, 1975. -- Amended 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 22, sec. 1. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 1241a-3.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Penalty if injury or death results from conspiracy -- Absence of malice no mitigation -- Civil liability.
